Hei.

72
00:04:56,537 --> 00:04:57,957
Sekarang, kau yang lebih dekat.

73
00:04:58,087 --> 00:05:00,417
Dia sungguh semena-mena.

74
00:05:00,877 --> 00:05:01,877
Sungguh.

75
00:05:01,967 --> 00:05:03,877
- Astaga.
- Apa kalian bertengkar lagi?

76
