125
00:09:50,037 --> 00:09:53,717
Ya. Benarkah?
Lee Eun-Soo di sini bersamaku.

126
00:09:53,797 --> 00:09:55,877
Ya.
Baiklah, jaga dirimu!

127
00:09:56,757 --> 00:09:58,467
- Apa?
