128
00:09:58,547 --> 00:10:00,177
tapi tidak bisa bicara lama.

129
00:10:00,257 --> 00:10:02,007
- Sayang sekali. Ya.
- Benarkah?

130
00:10:06,227 --> 00:10:08,557
Ketemu.
Ini, ya?

131
00:10:08,687 --> 00:10:10,857
- Ya.
