132
00:10:10,937 --> 00:10:11,937
Baiklah.

133
00:10:16,397 --> 00:10:18,027
Itu pasti Han Sun-Woo!

134
00:10:18,657 --> 00:10:21,577
Aku tahu dia akan meneleponku.

135
00:10:21,657 --> 00:10:23,237
